title: NO COUGAR - A League of Legends Video

embed.description: Hey guys, my name is Kid W25, and today we have some more League of Legends. In this video, I play a bit of ARAM with my brother Lukas and his friend.

body:
So since you guys loved my last post about my latest League video, I thought I would inform you of another one I just put up on my channel. First time Sona. ARAM. It was fun. She's a fun champ.

So if you can spare a few minutes, why don't you go and have a looksie and give me thoughts.

Cheers guys.

Kid.
